import React from 'react';
import { Container, Row, Col, Card, Button, Form, InputGroup, FormControl } from 'react-bootstrap';
import CustomNavbar from "./generics/CustomNavbar";
import PhoneInput from 'react-phone-number-input';
import 'react-phone-number-input/style.css';

const ProfilePage = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
            <CustomNavbar/>
            <Row className="justify-content-md-center mt-5">
                <Col md={8}>
                    <Card>
                        <Card.Body>
                            <Form>
                                <Row>
                                    <Col>
                                        <Form.Group controlId="firstName">
                                            <Form.Label>First Name</Form.Label>
                                            <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Enter your first name" />
                                        </Form.Group>
                                    </Col>
                                    <Col>
                                        <Form.Group controlId="lastName">
                                            <Form.Label>Last Name</Form.Label>
                                            <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Enter your last name" />
                                        </Form.Group>
                                    </Col>
                                </Row>
                                <Form.Group controlId="username">
                                    <Form.Label>Username</Form.Label>
                                    <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Enter your username" />
                                </Form.Group>
                                <Form.Group controlId="email">
                                    <Form.Label>Email</Form.Label>
                                    <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" />
                                </Form.Group>
                                <Form.Group controlId="phoneNumber">
                                    <Form.Label>Phone Number</Form.Label>
                                    <InputGroup>
                                        <Form.Group controlId="phoneNumber">
                                            <Form.Label>Phone Number</Form.Label>
                                            <PhoneInput
                                                placeholder="Enter your phone number"
                                                value={phone}
                                                onChange={setPhone}
                                                defaultCountry="US" // Set the default country code
                                            />
                                        </Form.Group>

                                    </InputGroup>
                                </Form.Group>
                                <Row className="justify-content-end">
                                    <Col xs={6} md={4} lg={3}>
                                        <Button variant="primary" type="submit" className="float-end">Save Changes</Button>
                                    </Col>
                                </Row>
                            </Form>
                        </Card.Body>
                    </Card>
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    );
}

export default ProfilePage;
